node.text:
Start your week off RIGHT with @wolfiesmom's sweet and salty no-bake bars! 😍🍫

Watch Valerie's #HomeCooking, Sundays at 11:30a|12:30c and subscribe to @discoveryplus to stream the entire series and so much more: https://links.discoveryplus.com/Y6O35sCeygb. #discoveryplus

Get the recipe: https://foodtv.com/3xEyay6 (Head to our IGTV to get the clickable links!)
